These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, potato, cherry
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, nurse, mechanic
1. the person eating corn is in an even position##4
2. the accountant is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
3. the accountant is the person eating potato##1
4. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1
5. the nurse is the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | cherry | corn | potato |
| Job    | nurse    | mechanic | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, collecting, singing
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, motorbike, airplane
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | collecting | singing | reading |
| Transport   | airplane    | motorbike     | train        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, reading, singing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, trance, house
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | singing     | reading | writing |
| Music-Genre   | trance | r&b     | house  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, epic, fantasy
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, tennis, rowing
1. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | epic  | comedy  |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | tennis | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, traveling, skydiving
There are 3 different nationalities: american, pakistani, italian
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the american##2
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
3. the italian is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | hiking   | skydiving | traveling    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | italian     | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, photography, gardening
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, golf, snowboarding
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | photography | gardening | rock-climbing   |
| Sport   | snowboarding     | badminton    | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, fantasy, mystery
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, chinchilla
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | thriller | fantasy |
| Pet           | bird         | hedgehog         | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, nectarine, cauliflower
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, pony
1. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the dog and the person eating eggplant##2
2. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | nectarine | cauliflower | eggplant |
| Pet    | dog    | chinchilla | pony     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, punk, soul
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, rowing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the fan of punk##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | punk  | indie  |
| Sport         | badminton | rowing | rugby |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: grapes, grapefruit, avocado
1. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person eating avocado is in an even position##4
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | mirinda      | fanta |
| Food       | grapefruit | avocado | grapes   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, architect, musician
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, ship, car
1. the musician is on the right of the architect##1
2. the person driving the van is the doctor##1
3. the person driving the car is the musician##1
4. the musician is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | architect | musician | doctor |
| Transport   | ship | car   | van |

