.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, british, malaysian
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, airplane, train
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the argentine is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the british##3
4. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | british | argentine |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus   | train        |

