.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, indian, russian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, basketball, golf
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the russian##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is the indian##1
3. the russian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Nationality   | russian  | argentine | indian   |
| Sport         | basketball | golf   | swimming |

