.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, dancing, chess
3 different pets are kept: rat, cat, hedgehog
1. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the owner of the cat##2
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | dancing | chess | camping |
| Pet     | rat    | hedgehog  | cat   |

