.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, action, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, trance, indie
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
3. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
4. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | superhero     | action |
| Music-Genre   | trance | d&b | indie    |

