.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, singing, baking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, techno, trance
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of soul is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | baking | reading   | singing |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | soul | trance      |

