.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, 7up
There are 3 different nationalities: british, indian, mexican
1. the mexican is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
2. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | sprite | 7up |
| Nationality   | indian   | mexican          | british |

