.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, goat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, rowing, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | lizard  | goat   | bird |
| Sport   | cricket | rowing | parkour       |

 